<br>
<br>
The disadvantage to is is what you have noticed : when you canny-pet using the 49 Earth or MS2 you get less mana/cast.<br>
<br>
The advantages are as follows:<br>
1)You can canny-pet with your combat pet. No need to mem a different pet spell for canny purposes.<br>
2)You can reclaim a near dead pet for just as much as you can do a fresh pet - this is extremely valuable in a pet centered group. If your pet is about to die, reclaim just before it dies, get back all of your mana and then summon another. Multiple mages working together can then take down any mob that can't kill every single pet engaging it in under 10 seconds, as mana ceases to be an issue.<br>
